<p>This is <strong>bold</strong> and this is <em>italic</em> text.</p>
<p>You can also use <u>underline</u> and <code>monospaced</code> words
in a line.</p>
<p>Markers combine, as in <strong><em>bold and italic</em></strong> and
<em>nested <strong>strong</strong> here</em>.</p>
